snippet.title: Dead Effect 2 - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The official release trailer for Dead Effect 2, one of the most anticipated mobile games of this year.

Dead Effect 2 is coming out on October 29, 2015 for Android and iOS.

For more information and the latest news about the game:
